T1  - The Evolution of Social Structure: Why Biology Matters
AU  - Pierce, Barbara Decker
AU  - White, Roderick
Y1  - 1999/10/01
PY  - 1999
DA  - 1999/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amr.1999.2553257
