N2  - The article comments on the articles ?The Relational View: Cooperative Strategy and Sources of Interorganizational Competitive Advantage,? by J. H. Dyer and H. Singh and ?Convergent Stakeholder Theory,? by T. M. Jones and A. C. Wicks. The authors of these two articles argue that organizational wealth can be increased through the fostering of stakeholder relationships. The author expands on this point by stating that one of the main goals of stakeholder management should be to enhance organizational wealth.
