N2  - The article presents a rebuttal to ?Convergent Stakeholder Theory,? by T. M. Jones and A. C. Wicks. The authors explain their reasoning behind suggesting their own phrase to represent the more commonly used ?stakeholder theory.? This alternative phrase was suggested because the word ?theory? seems over-used to the authors and they feel that an alternative term will offer clarification to nonstakeholder researchers. The authors also explain that there are tensions within the stakeholder aspect of management that make integration efforts challenging.
